<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/404497-are-you-excited-about-the-upcoming-movie">Are you excited about the upcoming movie? And what do you think of Christian Bale as Travis? I love Mr. McGee, he&#39;s an old school stand up guy, prehistorically over-protective of women but lovable none the less. Rosamund Pike is playing Lois, with Peter Dinklage on as McGee&#39;s buddy at Bahia Mar, Meyer. Follow along with me at my book-to-movie blog if you&#39;re interested.http://bit.ly/1FOcTl4</a>
</div>
