<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Bale couldn&apos;t pull off McGee. DiCaprio certainly couldn&apos;t. Kind of glad the movie didn&apos;t get made with those guys. James Garner could have done it. Ji<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Bale couldn't pull off McGee. DiCaprio certainly couldn't. Kind of glad the movie didn't get made with those guys. James Garner could have done it. Jim Rockford was modeled after McGee in the first place. Robert Mitchum could have. A younger Sean Connery would have been ideal, if he could have done an American accent believably. No one working today would fit. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
